 Each message is an 
\emph on
effect, 
\emph default
and every message the sending actor has previously sent or received is a
 
\emph on
cause 
\emph default
of that effect.
 Messaging
\emph on
 
\emph default
is causal if every cause is enqueued before the effect
\emph on
.
 
\emph default
