 This is a garbage collection rule, allowing 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha$
\end_inset

 to return that weight to 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha'$
\end_inset

 in the form of a 
\emph on
DEC
\emph default
 message.
\end_layout

